1️⃣1️⃣ CONCLUSION
The Employee Management System successfully implements RESTful APIs using Express.js and MongoDB.
It supports CRUD operations, multiple collections, relationship handling, and proper API testing.
The project fulfills all requirements of the Full Stack Development subject.

